    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >2023年初春风靡日本的<br>物理演算游戏里程碑——《Q REMASTERED》终于登陆Steam平台！</h2>这是一款用你的画笔来解开谜题的游戏，<br>收录了看似简单，实则需要费点心思的1200多道谜题。<br>解法无穷，充满自由！<br><br>本次Steam版本增设全新功能<br>诊断模式“Q TEST”！！！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246110/extras/7bbfdb088d6eb951f31ac9dece675d03.poster.avif?t=1743773578\" width=640 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246110/extras/7bbfdb088d6eb951f31ac9dece675d03.webm?t=1743773578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246110/extras/7bbfdb088d6eb951f31ac9dece675d03.mp4?t=1743773578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你的“Q之IQ”是多少？<br><br>“Q TEST”模式能够可视化你的IQ数值，<br>只需游玩专设关卡，游戏就能计算你的“Q之IQ”，并生成分析图表。<br><br>你能够从杯子里取出小球吗？<br>你能够让小球接触墙面吗？<br>嗯？你问我在说些什么？<br>如果你足够自信，不妨来挑战一下吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246110/extras/c402f4be6f0708b2bae76a27a2245f1b.poster.avif?t=1743773578\" width=640 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246110/extras/c402f4be6f0708b2bae76a27a2245f1b.webm?t=1743773578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246110/extras/c402f4be6f0708b2bae76a27a2245f1b.mp4?t=1743773578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏可使用鼠标键盘操作，跟着感觉走也能开心游玩。<br>当然游戏也支持手柄和SteamDeck触摸屏操作，在各种环境下都能过关斩将！<br>除此之外更是新增大量高难度成就，挑战性更上一层楼！！",
